headline: 1 Software Stock with Exciting Potential and 2 We Brush Off
summary: From commerce to culture, software is digitizing every aspect of our lives. Companies bringing it to life have been rewarded with high valuation multiples that make fundraising easier, but they have capped returns lately as the industry’s six-month gain of 15.3% has trailed the S&P 500’s 22.9%.
